[SAY] Now you can see special markers. Tabs show as a chevron, trailing spaces appear as dashes, and non-breaking spaces show as plus signs.
[SAY] This is useful for catching whitespace issues. To turn it off, use set nolist.
[TYPE] ':set nolist'

